metadata.name: ESSENCE_of_Checks//
metadata.description:
"ESSENCE//" by Fvckrender meets "Checks - VV" by Jack Butcher.

Friendly reminder: ESSENCE// can be burned for FVCK_AVATARS//... which are used to generate LVCIDIA// Resources... that can be used to craft LVCIDIA// Stars and Planets...

Now you're thinking: either there's going to be a burn mechanism with this or they're just promoting LVCIDIA and pumping their bags... or both.

And we're not gonna stop you from thinking about that.
